<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>DNASPEC - 基于三大技能的全生命周期避坑指南</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            background-attachment: fixed;
        }

        .container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2980b9 0%, #8e44ad 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 4rem 0;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        header:before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 50px 50px;
            opacity: 0.4;
        }

        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #ffffff, #f1c40f);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto 2rem;
            color: #ecf0f1;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            color: #bdc3c7;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        nav {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            padding: 1rem 0;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            list-style: none;
        }

        .nav-links li {
            margin: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
            padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 25px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        main {
            min-height: calc(100vh - 250px);
        }

        section {
            padding: 5rem 0;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
        }

        section:nth-child(even) {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);
        }

        section h2 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            color: #2c3e50;
            position: relative;
            padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        section h2:after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 120px;
            height: 5px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #3498db, #9b59b6);
            border-radius: 3px;
        }

        .intro {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto 3rem;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .avoidance-strategies {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 3rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }

        .strategy-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            border-left: 6px solid #e67e22;
            transition: transform 0.4s ease, box-shadow 0.4s ease;
        }

        .strategy-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-12px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        .strategy-card h3 {
            color: #d35400;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.6rem;
        }

        .strategy-card p {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: #666;
        }

        .strategy-card ul {
            margin-left: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .strategy-card li {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
        }

        .skill-application {
            background-color: #ecf0f1;
        }

        .skill-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
            gap: 2.5rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }

        .skill-card {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
            border-left: 5px solid #3498db;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .skill-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
        }

        .skill-card h3 {
            color: #2980b9;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
        }

        .skill-card h4 {
            color: #e74c3c;
            margin: 1.5rem 0 0.8rem;
        }

        .skill-card p {
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .example-box {
            background-color: #e8f4fd;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 1.2rem 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
            overflow-x: auto;
        }

        .example-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2980b9;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .example-code {
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            background: #2c3e50;
            color: #ecf0f1;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 0.8rem 0;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            white-space: pre-wrap;
        }

        .phase-label {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #3498db;
            color: white;
            padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin: 0 0.5rem 0.5rem 0;
        }

        .integration-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8e44ad 0%, #3498db 100%);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 5rem 0;
        }

        .integration-section h2 {
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .integration-section p {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto 2rem;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: #ecf0f1;
        }

        .case-studies-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(400px, 1fr));
            gap: 3rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }

        .case-study-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 2.8rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            color: #333;
            border-left: 5px solid #f39c12;
        }

        .case-study-card h3 {
            color: #d35400;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .case-study-card p {
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
        }

        .implementation-steps {
            background: white;
        }

        .steps-list {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 2rem auto;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .step-item {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border-left: 5px solid #9b59b6;
        }

        .step-item:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .step-item h4 {
            color: #8e44ad;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .step-item p {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .step-item ul {
            margin-left: 1.2rem;
        }

        .step-item li {
            margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
        }

        .summary-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2980b9 0%, #8e44ad 100%);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 5rem 0;
        }

        .summary-section h2 {
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .summary-section p {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto 2rem;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .page-links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .page-link {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f1c40f, #e67e22);
            color: white;
            padding: 0.8rem 1.8rem;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(241, 196, 15, 0.3);
        }

        .page-link:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(241, 196, 15, 0.5);
        }

        footer {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50 0%, #34495e 100%);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3rem 0;
        }

        .footer-content p {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            header h1 {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }

            header p {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }

            section h2 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .nav-links {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }

            .nav-links li {
                margin: 0.3rem 0;
            }

            .avoidance-strategies,
            .skill-grid,
            .case-studies-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>DNASPEC全生命周期避坑指南</h1>
            <p>基于三大核心技能的任务分解、约束生成和API检查，实现从简单到复杂系统的平稳演进</p>
            <p class="subtitle">以格式塔认知原则为指导，防止上下文爆炸、需求偏离和架构失控</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <nav>
        <ul class="nav-links">
            <li><a href="#intro">避坑概述</a></li>
            <li><a href="#strategies">避坑策略</a></li>
            <li><a href="#skills">技能应用</a></li>
            <li><a href="#integration">系统集成</a></li>
            <li><a href="#casestudies">案例研究</a></li>
            <li><a href="#implementation">实施路径</a></li>
            <li><a href="#summary">总结</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <main>
        <!-- 避坑概述 -->
        <section id="intro" class="section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>AI辅助开发中的常见陷阱与避坑策略</h2>
                <p class="intro">在系统从简单Idea到复杂智能化系统的全生命周期发展中，AI辅助开发面临众多陷阱。本指南详细阐述如何使用DNASPEC的三大核心技能（任务分解、约束生成、API检查）来避免这些陷阱，确保系统平稳演进。</p>
                
                <div class="intro">
                    <p>传统AI开发过程容易陷入上下文爆炸、需求偏离初心、架构失控等问题。通过智能技能系统，我们可以实现上下文隔离、宪法约束和分层对齐，打造真正的综合集成研讨厅架构。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 避坑策略 -->
        <section id="strategies" class="section strategies">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>核心避坑策略</h2>
                <div class="avoidance-strategies">
                    <div class="strategy-card">
                        <h3>1. 防止上下文爆炸</h3>
                        <p>通过任务分解技能创建独立工作区，确保每个子任务有独立的上下文空间，避免全局上下文膨胀。结合模块化技能实现功能模块的上下文隔离。</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>使用 /dnaspec.task-decomposer 创建原子任务工作区</li>
                            <li>限制单个任务的复杂度和上下文范围</li>
                            <li>通过智能体架构避免全局上下文污染</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="strategy-card">
                        <h3>2. 防止需求偏离初心</h3>
                        <p>建立宪法需求版本管理体系，所有新需求必须与初始宪法需求对齐。通过约束生成技能持续监控需求的一致性，防止需求碎片化和偏离。</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>使用 /dnaspec.constraint-generator 锁定初始需求宪法</li>
                            <li>持续验证新需求与宪法的对齐性</li>
                            <li>建立需求变更的追溯和审批机制</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="strategy-card">
                        <h3>3. 防止架构失控</h3>
                        <p>通过API检查技能实现分层审核，确保模块级、子系统级、系统级的接口一致性。使用架构师技能设计可扩展的系统结构，防止架构混乱。</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>使用 /dnaspec.api-checker 实现多层级接口对齐</li>
                            <li>确保模块间接口的清晰定义和验证</li>
                            <li>建立层级间的调用规范和约束</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="strategy-card">
                        <h3>4. 防止任务不对齐</h3>
                        <p>通过认知模板技能和任务分解技能，确保从顶层目标到底层任务的一致性。使用格式塔认知原则，保持系统各部分的统一性和连贯性。</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>应用认知模板保持任务结构一致性</li>
                            <li>验证任务分解的目标对齐性</li>
                            <li>检查任务间依赖关系的合理性</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="strategy-card">
                        <h3>5. 防止逻辑不一致</h3>
                        <p>在定性定量处理间建立统一的验证机制，确保系统整体逻辑一致性。通过格式塔原则的连续性原则，保持逻辑链条的完整性。</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>验证定性部分与定量部分的一致性</li>
                            <li>检测系统各模块的逻辑冲突</li>
                            <li>建立统一的逻辑验证标准</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="strategy-card">
                        <h3>6. 防止模块间混乱</h3>
                        <p>通过模块化技能和API检查技能，确保各模块有明确边界和清晰接口。防止模块间过度耦合和功能混乱。</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>使用 /dnaspec.modulizer 定义模块边界</li>
                            <li>验证模块间的接口一致性</li>
                            <li>建立模块交互的规范和协议</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 技能应用 -->
        <section id="skills" class="section skills">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>三大核心技能全生命周期应用</h2>
                <p class="intro">详细阐述任务分解、约束生成、API检查三项技能在系统演进各阶段的具体应用和避坑效果</p>

                <div class="skill-grid">
                    <div class="skill-card">
                        <h3>任务分解技能 (/dnaspec.task-decomposer)</h3>
                        <p>遵循KISS、YAGNI、SOLID原则，将复杂需求分解为原子任务，并创建独立工作区防止上下文爆炸，实现任务级别的隔离和独立性。</p>

                        <h4>在各阶段的应用:</h4>
                        <div class="phase-label">Idea阶段</div>将模糊概念分解为具体可行的初步任务
                        <div class="phase-label">需求阶段</div>将功能需求分解为可执行的独立任务
                        <div class="phase-label">细化阶段</div>将复杂功能细化为原子任务，创建隔离工作区
                        <div class="phase-label">智能阶段</div>为智能体创建分解专门任务

                        <div class="example-box">
                            <div class="example-title">使用示例:</div>
                            <div class="example-code">/dnaspec.task-decomposer "构建电商平台" --max-depth 3</div>
                        </div>

                        <p><strong>避坑效果:</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>防止任务爆炸 - 限制任务数量和复杂度</li>
                            <li>上下文隔离 - 每个任务有独立工作区</li>
                            <li>职责明确 - 任务边界清晰，避免重复</li>
                            <li>遵循原则 - 保持KISS/YAGNI/SOLID原则</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="skill-card">
                        <h3>约束生成技能 (/dnaspec.constraint-generator)</h3>
                        <p>基于宪法级初始需求生成动态约束，实现需求版本管理和时间点恢复机制，确保后续需求与初始目标对齐，防止需求偏离初心。</p>

                        <h4>在各阶段的应用:</h4>
                        <div class="phase-label">Idea阶段</div>锁定初始需求为宪法版本
                        <div class="phase-label">需求阶段</div>生成新需求与宪法的对齐约束
                        <div class="phase-label">细化阶段</div>监控功能实现与宪法的一致性
                        <div class="phase-label">智能阶段</div>确保智能体行为符合宪法约束

                        <div class="example-box">
                            <div class="example-title">使用示例:</div>
                            <div class="example-code">/dnaspec.constraint-generator "用户认证系统核心需求" --change-request "添加生物识别认证"</div>
                        </div>

                        <p><strong>避坑效果:</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>宪法锁定 - 初始需求不可随意更改</li>
                            <li>对齐检查 - 新需求与宪法保持一致</li>
                            <li>冲突检测 - 及时发现需求冲突</li>
                            <li>时间恢复 - 支持需求变更回滚</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="skill-card">
                        <h3>API检查技能 (/dnaspec.api-checker)</h3>
                        <p>实现模块级、子系统级、系统级的分级审核，验证多层级间的调用对齐和作用域管理，确保各层级接口一致性。</p>

                        <h4>在各阶段的应用:</h4>
                        <div class="phase-label">Idea阶段</div>定义API级别的初始结构
                        <div class="phase-label">需求阶段</div>验证功能模块间的接口对齐
                        <div class="phase-label">细化阶段</div>检查子系统级接口一致性
                        <div class="phase-label">智能阶段</div>确保智能体API符合多层级规范

                        <div class="example-box">
                            <div class="example-title">使用示例:</div>
                            <div class="example-code">/dnaspec.api-checker "验证用户服务与认证服务接口对齐" --level module</div>
                        </div>

                        <p><strong>避坑效果:</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>分级审核 - 按模块、子系统、系统级验证</li>
                            <li>多级对齐 - 确保各层级间接口一致</li>
                            <li>作用域管理 - 控制全局到局部的作用域</li>
                            <li>架构稳定 - 防止接口混乱导致架构失控</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 系统集成 -->
        <section id="integration" class="integration-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>综合集成研讨厅架构集成</h2>
                <p>在综合集成研讨厅架构下，定性定量处理方式有机结合，通过局部智能体处理不确定性，通过代码固化确定性逻辑，通过宪法需求确保系统一致性，通过分级审核实现多层级对齐。</p>
                
                <p>这种架构不仅避免了AI开发中的常见陷阱，还实现了真正的智能化自动增长，支持从简单Idea到复杂智能体系统的平稳演进。系统遵循格萨塔认知完整性原则，确保用户在与系统交互时感受到统一连贯的体验。</p>
                
                <div class="intro">
